sequenceDiagram
    participant vLLM as vLLM Pod<br/>ZMQ PUB 5557/TCP
    participant ZMQSub as ZMQ Subscriber<br/>(per-pod)
    participant Pool as KV Events Pool<br/>(sharded workers)
    participant Adapter as Engine Adapter<br/>(vLLM/SGLang)
    participant Index as KV Block Index<br/>(LRU/Ristretto/Redis)
    participant Scheduler as llm-d-inference-scheduler
    participant Indexer as KV-Cache Indexer
    participant TokenPool as Tokenization Pool
    participant UDS as UDS Tokenizer<br/>gRPC over UDS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Storage as Shared Storage<br/>NFS/PVC
    participant FSBackend as FS Backend<br/>(vLLM plugin)

    Note over vLLM,Index: Flow 1: KV-Event Ingestion (Write Path)
    vLLM->>ZMQSub: BlockStored/BlockRemoved event<br/>ZMQ 3-frame (topic, seq#, msgpack)
    ZMQSub->>Pool: Route to worker<br/>FNV-1a(podID) % shards
    Pool->>Adapter: Decode event payload<br/>msgpack
    Adapter->>Index: Add/Evict block<br/>hash → pod location

    Note over Scheduler,UDS: Flow 2: Pod Scoring (Read Path)
    Scheduler->>Indexer: GetPodScores(request)<br/>in-process call
    Indexer->>TokenPool: Tokenize prompt
    TokenPool->>UDS: gRPC Tokenize()<br/>Unix Domain Socket
    UDS-->>TokenPool: Token IDs + offsets
    Note over UDS,HF: First use: download tokenizer
    UDS->>HF: GET model tokenizer<br/>HTTPS 443, Bearer Token (opt)
    HF-->>UDS: Tokenizer files
    TokenPool-->>Indexer: Token IDs
    Indexer->>Indexer: Compute block keys<br/>CBOR + FNV-64a chained hash
    Indexer->>Index: Lookup block locations
    Index-->>Indexer: Pod → block mappings
    Indexer->>Indexer: Score pods<br/>(longest prefix match)
    Indexer-->>Scheduler: Pod scores[]

    Note over vLLM,Storage: Flow 3: KV-Cache Offloading (Storage Path)
    vLLM->>FSBackend: OffloadingSpec lookup
    FSBackend->>Storage: stat() check<br/>hash-based directory hierarchy
    Storage-->>FSBackend: File exists/missing
    vLLM->>FSBackend: Transfer request
    FSBackend->>Storage: Async write (C++ engine)<br/>POSIX I/O or NVIDIA GDS
    Storage-->>FSBackend: Write complete

    Note over Storage,Storage: Flow 4: PVC Eviction
    Note right of Storage: Activator: statvfs() polling<br/>Threshold: 85% cleanup / 70% target<br/>N crawlers: hex-based load balancing<br/>Deleter: xargs -0 rm -f batches
